# .stowrc
#
# Purpose:
#   Default GNU Stow settings when you run `stow ...` manually.
#
# Why target=..:
#   This repository is intended to live at `~/.dotfiles`.
#   When you are inside `~/.dotfiles`, the parent directory (`..`) is `$HOME`.
#   This makes `stow common` behave like `stow -t "$HOME" common`.
#
# Reference:
#   - GNU Stow manual: <https://www.gnu.org/software/stow/manual/stow.html>

target=..
